Name: Angstrage
About the game: -Angstrage is a simple 2D platform game full of traps, which tests your patience. No checkpoint, no bonuses, nothing extra only your dexterity and patience matter. If you think you have it in you, put yourself to the test and take it all the way. -If you like rage games, then you are in the right place. Angstrage is a simple rage game with 10 levels full of hidden traps .The game has a bit of an old vibe, the graphics and controls are also simple but still very enjoyable. Good Fun or Rage !
